{"prompt": "Develop a site for a performance art collective. The visuals should be avant-garde and include a marigold yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Avant-Garde Collective</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f8f0e3; /* Soft off-white */\n            color: #333;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #f9a602; /* Marigold Yellow */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 2rem 1rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            letter-spacing: 0.2rem;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .gradient-bar {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 20px;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f9a602, #e68a00); /* Marigold to a darker orange */\n        }\n        main {\n            flex: 1;\n            padding: 2rem 1rem;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 2rem;\n        }\n        .content-block {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border: 2px solid #f9a602; /* Marigold border */\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            width: 300px;\n            box-shadow: 5px 5px 0px #e68a00; /* Darker orange shadow */\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .content-block:hover {\n            transform: translate(-5px, -5px);\n            box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px #e68a00;\n        }\n        .content-block h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #e68a00; /* Darker orange */\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            border-bottom: 1px dashed #f9a602;\n            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n        .content-block p {\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #f8f0e3;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 1rem;\n            margin-top: auto;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        /* Avant-garde visual elements */\n        .header-blob {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50px;\n            left: -50px;\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 200px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n        .content-block::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 10px;\n            right: 10px;\n            width: 30px;\n            height: 30px;\n            background-color: rgba(230, 138, 0, 0.2); /* Transparent darker orange */\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"header-blob\"></div>\n        <h1>The Unseen Echo</h1>\n        <p>Performance Art Collective</p>\n    </header>\n    <div class=\"gradient-bar\"></div>\n    <main>\n        <section class=\"content-block\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>We are a collective dedicated to pushing the boundaries of human expression through raw, unfiltered performance. Our work explores themes of identity, societal constructs, and the ephemeral nature of existence.</p>\n        </section>\n        <section class=\"content-block\">\n            <h2>Current Works</h2>\n            <p>Explore our latest provocations and performances. Details on upcoming events and past archives available.</p>\n        </section>\n        <section class=\"content-block\">\n            <h2>Contact</h2>\n            <p>Connect with us for collaborations, inquiries, or to join the conversation. Let's create something extraordinary together.</p>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 The Unseen Echo. All rights reserved. Created with audacious spirit.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}